*Zvala* je njega da dođe na rođendan. (She called him to come to the birthday party.)

Ona je *zvala* da se javi. (She called to respond.)

*Zvala* je svoje prijatelje. (She was calling her friends.)

On je *zvao* nju da ide sa njim. (He was calling her to go with him.)

*Zvao* je svoju sestru da mu pomogne. (He was calling his sister to help him.)